  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Combined Husky &amp; Reindeer Safari</h2>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" align="right" style="width: 343px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="center" valign="top"><img src="/media/13052631/reindeer-safari.jpg" alt="Reindeer Safari" width="343" height="202" align="left" rel="621,366" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>An animal lover's dream and a great value excursion that makes the most of your valuable holiday time. <br /><br />Meet some of Santa's reindeer deep in their silent forest hideaway. Learn about their way of life from colourful local Sámi herders and enjoy a romantic reindeer sleigh ride for 1½km across the snowy landscape. Delicious hot fruit juice and cake will be served. Next it's time to visit the huskies in their nearby cosy wilderness home. Learn about their way of life while huddled around a campfire inside a traditional Lappish Kota hut. Enjoy a 2km dog-sled ride through the sparkling winter landscape.<br /><br /></p>
<p><strong>Total excursion duration</strong> approx 2½hrs.</p>
<p><em><strong>Please note:</strong> We act as at all times as the selling agent for the supplier of excursions and activities. Times and distances are approximate and may vary due to weather conditions. Child excursion age is 2-12yrs in Levi and 4-12 in Ylläs. Infants are <strong>Free</strong> but will be required to pre-book for transportation to the reindeer &amp; husky safari.</em></p>
<div class="hr hr-spaced"></div>
<h2>Snowmobile Safari</h2>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" align="right" style="width: 343px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="center" valign="top"><img src="/media/13052634/snowmobile-safari-th.jpg" alt="Reindeer Safari" width="343" height="202" align="left" rel="621,366" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Experience an exhilarating 25km ride through beautiful scenery, snow-laden forests and frozen lakes.<br /><br />Snowmobiles are easy to drive on your own or sharing with a passenger. Children either share with an adult or are towed in a covered sled behind the guide (kids sleds are not covered in Ylläs).<br /><br />Total excursion duration approx 2½hrs.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><br /><br /><em><strong>Please note:</strong> We act as at all times as the selling agent for the supplier of excursions and activities. Times and distances are approximate and may vary due to weather conditions. <span>Snowmobile child age is 4-12yrs. Infants can pay a fixed charge for transport to and from the excursion but are not allowed on Super Reindeer, Super Husky or any Snowmobile safaris</span>. On Inghams, and most other travel policies, cover is provided for personal and medical expenses but not for damage to the snowmobile itself. Snowmobile drivers must be 18yrs old and bring a full driver's license with them. Insurance is included by the snowmobile company for damage to the snowmobile or to third parties and their property but please note there is an insurance excess of approximately 850 Euro in Levi and 850 Euro in Ylläs payable directly to the excursion provider.</em></p>]]></bodyText>
